Package gUI

Class Summary
CloseListener A listener class to be attached to close buttons to close the window it is a part of.
ContestRunner A class used for running a new contest in a new thread.
ContestWindow This class displays the window that allows the user to set up a contest.
GameDisplay This class is the Processing Sketch which displays the ant world to the screen in the main window.
GUIErrorMsg Simple class used to display error messages to the user.
LiveStatGrabber A class for retrieving statistics from the current game and updating the main window with them.
MainWindow This class displays the main window GUI.
SimulationRunner Used for running a new simulation in a new thread.
StatisticsWindow Represents a window that displays the statistics from a regular game once it is finished.
WorldGenerateWindow This class displays the window which allows the user to specify how a world is generated.
 

Enum Summary
DisplayStates Enumeration of the different states the game display can be in.
